##Yiwu hard-core resumption of work: The daily flow of more than 200,000 people to open the city of trade

"knock, knock, knock... "

The opening ceremony of Yiwu International Trade City was held at 9 am on February 18 as usual, but this year the performers all wore masks and the number of spectators was greatly reduced.

Yiwu International Trade City, with a total business area of more than 4 million square meters, is one of the largest export bases for small commodities in China.

Affected by the epidemic, the first trading city of the only one and two districts, the other three districts of the opening time is not clear.

As of February 18, there had been no new cases of coronary pneumonia in Yiwu for six consecutive days, the epidemic was well under control, and the International Trade City opened three days earlier than scheduled. This is still the longest holiday for business owners.

The first commercial and Trade City area has five business areas: main market, direct sales center of Production Enterprises, commodity purchase center, Storage Center and catering center. There are more than 9000 shops and more than 11000 households District 2 mainly engaged in hardware, electronics, electrical appliances, luggage, rain gear, watches and other 6 industries, a total of more than 8000 business, operating more than 10,000 households.

Wang Huafu, the owner of a natural road shop in the first district of Yiwu International Trade City, who works in the handicraft business, is from Taizhou, a major area of the epidemic. Although he has no close contacts, he also completed a 14-day quarantine and passed a health declaration before the opening of the market.

On the day of the opening of the market, he went through the checkpoint to the shop, cleaned the floor, cleaned the samples and started the first day of the year of the rat. Wang Huafu is not worried about the prevention and control of the epidemic in the city of commerce and trade. "There are special workers in the market who are responsible for killing, and every corner is involved, " he told interface news.

Wang Huafu's shop mainly do domestic sales business, because other provincial capital guests are still difficult to come in, logistics is not fully open, his business has been some impact. But on the first day of trading, buyers still placed several orders through online platforms such as Wechat. He remains confident of this year's market and says "business will still be better when the epidemic is over" .

In addition to managing his own shop, Wang Huafu, as vice president of the Craft Chamber of Commerce and Trade City, is also a volunteer in the prevention and control of the epidemic. Specifically, he is responsible for checking whether the operators and buyers in zone D on the 4th floor wear face masks, gather to chat, etc. , if a business owner needs help, he has to go ahead and help.

According to the introduction of Wang Huafu, the first day of the market, the city of Commerce and trade crafts industry opening rate of more than 50% .

Tao Xiaoyan of pottery craft shop does adorn article business, before opening five or six days, she made good health declaration. On the first day of trading, she received a domestic order for more than $10,000 from a local customer in Jinhua. At the same time, Tao Xiaoyan also received more than 10 orders online, starting the first day of orders a total of more than 100,000.

Tao Xiaoyan told interface news that the last few days of the opening of the market were busy seasons. This year, the opening of the market was affected by the epidemic. The list was much less than in previous years. Although not satisfied, there were orders that were also quite ideal.

Like many commodity city operators, Tao Xiaoyan's jewelry business also relies on the "front shop behind the factory" model. Although the store is open, her factory has not yet resumed work.

Tao's accessories factory has more than 100 employees, most of whom have private cars, both in Jinhua and among migrant workers in Guizhou and Henan provinces. In the next few days, most of these employees will drive their private cars to Yiwu to resume work, and Tao will report government travel subsidies to the employees.

According to Tao Xiaoyan, there are 6,000 to 7,000 stalls in the Jewelry Trade Association, and the current opening rate is 60% to 70% .

Ding Xingjuan is a district accessories industry shop owner. In her shop, 30% are for export and 70% are for domestic sales. The first day of opening, her total order amount is only 100,000, and are domestic trade orders.

Their biggest difficulty is that the factory has not resumed work. Only a few dozen of the more than 300 workers have come. The workers have long wanted to resume work, but some towns in the interior do not allow residents to go out.

The situation in the second district of Yiwu International Trade City is similar to that in the first district. Zhang Jiying, the owner of a rain gear shop, has been working hard in Yiwu for more than 20 years. She has always kept in mind her father's lesson of "watch the shop and never leave the counter" . As long as the market is open, jane Chang has no weekends, no holidays. This year's Spring Festival is the longest Zhang has ever taken because of the epidemic.

The market opened normally and operators and buyers were able to enter the mall in an orderly manner. Zhang said the Yiwu municipal government and the Mall Group had done a lot of work and had withstood great pressure.

Her rain gear shop is 80% foreign trade single, the first day of the market, many customers through wechat video style, but whether online or physical shop orders today, 100,000, the order volume is not large, at least double the order volume in previous years.

However, Ms Zhang's sales staff have been working online since the 12th day of the Lunar New Year, with more than 1m orders on hand. Jane Chang was quite satisfied with the present state of affairs.

Her factory, which employs more than 100 people, is in the process of applying to resume work. Because inventory has a certain amount of stock, on the whole rain gear shop business is not affected by the factory has not resumed work.

Zhang Jiying thinks a shop can not prop up a commodity market, hope epidemic as early as possible past, only everybody good is really good.

In the epidemic prevention and Control Management, "the smallest unit control" is implemented in the city, that is, each store is a cell, merchants to store buyers Qr Code Verification or Information Registration, to ensure traceability; Each "control unit" is made up of nine cells (nine business units) , which are used for rapid control of anomalies.

According to the trade city data, the market 495 party members, 32 party branches, 6 Support Business Alliance team, carry out precision "unit combat" , and timely do a good job of dispute mediation, red and other services.

Operators and buyers also have careful security arrangements to get in and out of the city. The Mall requires operators and buyers to fill out the health declaration form through the "righteous credit purchase" mini-program. A Green Qr code is considered as a sign that the operator or buyer is in good health. With a Qr Code, an identity card, and after passing a temperature test, operators and buyers can enter the trade city.

In order to disperse the flow of people to achieve optimal prevention and control, the opening of the international trade city, zone 1 and 2, a total of 16 entrances, each entrance is equipped with infrared, line thermometer and other intelligent equipment.

To get the market moving as soon as possible, the city of commerce and trade will, on the one hand, reduce or waive the rent for business spaces during the extended opening period, and provide financing and blood transfusion for import enterprises; on the other hand, fully guarantee catering, accommodation, foreign trade, logistics, customs clearance, finance and other supporting industry chain services for the opening of the market, and provide all-round food, lodging, transportation and Foreign Trade Services for the buyers of Laiyi, foreign buyers coming to Yiwu for the first time can also enjoy 3 days of free accommodation in the group's hotels.

Mall Protection Measures and compensation measures are doing well, but from the above description of the city's owners, the factory did not return to work directly affect the business owners of the city orders.

Yiwu International Trade City itself involves a wide range of industries, the opening of Yiwu International Trade City can drive more industry chain recovery.

Taking the mid-stream logistics industry as an example, Yiwu's express delivery volume totaled 5.922 billion pieces in 2019, ranking second in the country after Guangzhou's 6.347 billion pieces.

An e-commerce told interface news, "fortunately opened, we help e-commerce is too hard, several hundred single pressure can not be shipped, some also have to fine. "

A local market official said the opening of Yiwu International Trade City could encourage enterprises and merchants in the chain of production and operation to resume production. But this is a very strong linkage marketing system, there is no relevant industry, especially downstream of the normal operation, especially the support of consumer terminals, even after the opening of the market situation is also not expected.

The owner of Yiwu Xintean Arts and crafts factory said that he had received more than 20 million yuan orders years ago, with an order of more than 180,000 US dollars for delivery by the end of March.

Returning to work is imminent. The problem is that most of the migrant workers in Yiwu are from other places.

According to official figures for 2016, Yiwu has a resident population of 1.978 M, of which nearly 1.2 m are non-residents of Yiwu, and migrant workers are the most important force in Yiwu's economy.

Yiwu Xintean Arts and crafts factory boss, the factory more than 500 employees, 80%-90% from Guizhou.

How to prevent and control the epidemic at the same time to do a good job of migrant workers to return to work in an orderly manner has become a difficult problem.

On February 13, Che Jun, Secretary of the CPC Zhejiang Provincial Committee, went to Jinhua to oversee the prevention and control of the epidemic and resume work. He stressed that the quiet to continue to quiet, let the move to move in an orderly manner, do their best to prevent and control the epidemic, actively and steadily promote the resumption of production.

Subsequently, Yiwu Guanwei released a message saying that the current prevention and control work of Xinguan pneumonia in our city has achieved positive results. Under the premise of ensuring that the epidemic situation can be controlled, we actively and orderly pushed enterprises to resume work and production, and worked hard to achieve the smooth operation of our city's economy and society, has become a priority. Meanwhile, the Yiwu Bureau of Human Resources and Social Welfare has issued 10 notices to ensure that enterprises return to work during the epidemic prevention and control period.

In order to make arrangements for migrant workers to resume work, relevant government departments in Yiwu on February 16 set up a resumption of work enterprises to return to work special classes. In the afternoon, six fully subsidized buses went to Red River, Guizhou Bijie and Suixi, Anhui Province, to greet employees who were returning to Yiwu.

In addition to the buses, the Yiwu municipal government sent 10 working groups to Henan, Anhui, Jiangxi, Shaanxi, Yunnan, Guizhou and other places to organize staff rework and recruit new employees.

It is worth mentioning that the Yiwu municipal government for the resumption of workers car travel subsidies. The municipal government shall fully subsidize the hire car expenses incurred by enterprises in picking up and dropping off employees from relatively concentrated places of origin by means of car chartering and car sharing among enterprises.

For the employees who returned to righteousness by themselves, the Enterprise Employees who came to righteousness by means of railway trains or passenger cars before February 22 shall be given a full subsidy for the ticket fee; for the Enterprise Employees who came to righteousness from February 23 to February 29, the subsidy shall be cut in half. For those who return before February 22, the subsidy will be given according to the standard of railway trains in the same area; for those who return between February 23 and February 29, the subsidy will be cut in half. First-time volunteer job seekers can also enjoy three days of free accommodation.

Up to now, the re-work rates of foreign trade enterprises over US $10 million, e-commerce enterprises over US $100 million and industrial enterprises under planning in Yiwu have reached 89.6% , 84% and 83.7% respectively, and 38 key projects such as Mall Avenue have been resumed in an orderly manner.
